    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/2dd26bdc4155d7f29e7bc0632db96227.apng?t=1726215934\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/2dd26bdc4155d7f29e7bc0632db96227.poster.avif?t=1726215934\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=128 /></picture></span><br><br>《Chronicles of 2 Heroes》是一款战斗节奏紧凑的 16 位动作跳台游戏，兼具恶魔城元素、日本神话色彩和华丽像素艺术。不仅如此，您还可随时在两位主角之间切换！彩女和剑圣各自均身怀绝技，您需身兼二人技艺，才能拯救封建时期之日本于天照大神暴政之水火。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/b1a0075c938c0d84169854ff2972e28c.poster.avif?t=1726215934\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/b1a0075c938c0d84169854ff2972e28c.webm?t=1726215934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/b1a0075c938c0d84169854ff2972e28c.mp4?t=1726215934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/a9dc6d2abcc266ba9655d255efaf4faa.poster.avif?t=1726215934\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/a9dc6d2abcc266ba9655d255efaf4faa.webm?t=1726215934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>随时在两位主角之间切换</strong>。剑圣擅武士刀贴身肉搏，但不会轻功。彩女则更加身轻如燕，擅长远程攻击。<br><br></li><li><strong>克服经典跳台游戏挑战</strong>。这款游戏基于经典跳台游戏风格，但也尝试为玩家带来了更令人惊叹、更加现代的体验。<br><br></li><li><strong>置身日本神话世界</strong>。对抗浪人、面具怪和其他源自日本神话的数不尽的敌人。<br><br></li><li><strong>解锁多达 20 种强大能力</strong>。从震地撼敌，到连跳飞高。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/83e7827664fde33c20bcc290c25359fa.poster.avif?t=1726215934\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/83e7827664fde33c20bcc290c25359fa.webm?t=1726215934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/83e7827664fde33c20bcc290c25359fa.mp4?t=1726215934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/a3f564fba1f8e3951fc802d762b91bb4.poster.avif?t=1726215934\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/a3f564fba1f8e3951fc802d762b91bb4.webm?t=1726215934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>天照大神和她的仆从卑弥呼女皇，凭借面具怪大军的力量暴虐统治着日本。所有的希望都落在了身为武士的剑圣和身为女忍的彩女这对兄妹身上，二人苦练多年，立志击败这位女神。兄妹齐心协力，闯进了大阪皇宫，盗得了女皇力量的来源——三圣物。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/bd4ad8e4b44c7a6a3b68634c7f30bad1.poster.avif?t=1726215934\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/bd4ad8e4b44c7a6a3b68634c7f30bad1.webm?t=1726215934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747560/extras/bd4ad8e4b44c7a6a3b68634c7f30bad1.mp4?t=1726215934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
